"title": "4938: fate, and final destiny",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "4938: fate, and final destiny",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The final destiny or predetermined end of individuals, groups or nations.</p>\n<h2>Death, the fate of humanity</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl7:2\">ECC 7:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl2:14-Eccl2:16\">ECC 2:14–2:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl3:19-Eccl3:22\">ECC 3:19–3:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl9:2-Eccl9:6\">ECC 9:2–9:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb9:27\">HEB 9:27</a></p>\n<h2>The fate of the ungodly</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa65:11-Isa65:12\">ISA 65:11–65:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job8:11-Job8:19\">JOB 8:11–8:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps49:13-Ps49:20\">PSA 49:13–49:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps73:17\">PSA 73:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:5-Eph5:6\">EPH 5:5–5:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet2:4-2Pet2:9\">2PE 2:4–2:9</a></p>\n<h2>The fate of the godly</h2>\n<h3>The fate of the godly in terms of God's rewards</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet1:10-2Pet1:11\">2PE 1:10–1:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:3-Matt5:10\">MAT 5:3–5:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt25:34\">MAT 25:34</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke6:20-Luke6:22\">LUK 6:20–6:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor2:7\">1CO 2:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:12\">JAS 1:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas2:5\">JAS 2:5</a></p>\n<h3>The fate of the godly in terms of present suffering</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim3:12\">2TI 3:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John15:20\">JHN 15:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess3:1-1Thess3:4\">1TH 3:1–3:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet4:12-1Pet4:14\">1PE 4:12–4:14</a></p>\n<h2>The fate of individuals</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke2:34-Luke2:35\">LUK 2:34–2:35</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs20:37-1Kgs20:42\">1KI 20:37–20:42</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs21:17-1Kgs21:26\">1KI 21:17–21:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke22:22\">LUK 22:22</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:24\">MAT 26:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark14:21\">MRK 14:21</a></p>\n<h2>The fate of human regulations, institutions and earthly realms</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan7:27\">DAN 7:27</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job12:23-Job12:25\">JOB 12:23–12:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa34:1-Isa34:4\">ISA 34:1–34:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan2:21\">DAN 2:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt24:35\">MAT 24:35</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark13:31\">MRK 13:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke21:33\">LUK 21:33</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col2:20-Col2:22\">COL 2:20–2:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev18:1-Rev18:3\">REV 18:1–18:3</a></p>",
